      "module_path": "pre_commit_type_signals",
      "docs": "DTO returned by PreCommitTypeSignalsService::run. frozen: bool is removed: the branch-based guard (IN-02, CN-04) rejects non-current-branch tracks before reaching this output stage, so callers no longer need a frozen flag. blocked: bool remains (red signals present). red_signals / yellow_signals carry free-text signal names — raw Vec<String> justified (opaque diagnostic labels, no domain constraint). Dto placed in usecase per R1 — pure pass-through DTO with no serde dependency, conveying use-case result across the usecase boundary.",
